nline-01.png","line":35,"embedded":true},{"title":"一个人站在分岔路口的插画，一条路指向屏幕和AI界面，另一条路指向一枚硬币，风格简洁现代","target":"imgs/inline-02.png","line":89,"embedded":true},{"title":"一组对比插画：左侧是被多个推荐气泡包围的人显得信息过载，右侧是手持硬币的人显得清晰从容，风格统一","target":"imgs/inline-03.png","line":141,"embedded":true},{"title":"Reddit帖子讨论的抽象可视化：社区围绕硬币聚集，远处是发光的AI界面，形成对比，扁平风格","target":"imgs/inline-04.png","line":191,"embedded":true},{"title":"Catalyzing decisions: How a coin flip strengthens affective reactions","target":"https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC6693849/","line":271},{"title":"Heads or Tails: The Impact of a Coin Toss on Major Life Decisions","target":"https://gwern.net/doc/psychology/cognitive-bias/2020-levitt.pdf","line":273},{"title":"Don't Leave Your Decision to Chance, Flip a Coin","target":"https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/time-travelling-apollo/201906/dont-leave-your-decision-chance-flip-coin","line":275},{"title":"From algorithm aversion to AI dependence: Deskilling, upskilling, and emerging addictions in the GenAI age","target":"https://myscp.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/arcp.70008","line":277},{"title":"When Autonomy Breaks: The Hidden Existential Risk of AI","target":"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00146-025-02397-5","line":279},{"title":"Algorithm Aversion","target":"https://thedecisionlab.com/reference-guide/psychology/algorithm-aversion","line":281},{"title":"AI Boss Effect Report","target":"https://www.resume-now.com/job-resources/careers/ai-boss-effect-report","line":283},{"title":"How People Use & Trust ChatGPT in 2025","target":"https://expresslegalfunding.com/chatgpt-study/","line":285},{"title":"A quarter of Gen Zers have followed ChatGPT's career advice","target":"https://fortune.com/2025/08/19/quarter-of-gen-z-have-followed-ai-chatgpt-career-advice-and-few-have-regrets/","line":287},{"title":"AI and the future of human decision-making","target":"https://www.deloitte.com/us/en/insights/topics/talent/human-capital-trends/2026/decision-making-with-ai.html","line":289}],"metadata":{"title":"硬币决策法击败AI：为什么越来越多人用抛硬币做决定","author":"GeekJourney","description":"当97%的人开始向AI求助人生决策时，Reddit上18000人却选择了抛硬币。这不是反智，而是人类在算法时代对自主判断力的本能捍卫。从心理学实验到社会现象，硬币决策法揭示了一个被忽视的真相：有些答案，只有你自己知道。","digest":"97%的人向AI求助人生决策，Reddit上18000人却选了抛硬币——这不是反智，是人类自主性最后的防线。","coverImage":"imgs/cover.png","styleMode":"deep-analysis","sourceType":"topic-research","structureFrame":"deep-analysis","disclosure":"本文由AI辅助研究和写作，基于公开学术论文、调查报告和社区数据。所有数据点均标注来源。人类提供了核心论点框架和编辑审核。"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:产出/公众号/2026-04/20260410-硬币决策法击败AI/article.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1mq17rc","at":1776170620313},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06231605,0.00692505,0.00540734,-0.04708256,0.04186755,0.01818031,-0.01207968,0.05078163,0.05746252,-0.02051155,0.00540647,-0.0149669,0.03362116,0.03009198,0.03530471,0.04715024,0.01357053,-0.0888991,-0.02834132,-0.02070273,0.15576714,-0.07934386,0.04508697,-0.11744233,-0.00243064,0.00116103,-0.02039205,-0.04173341,-0.00621191,-0.14106978,-0.03712723,-0.04001635,0.09766135,0.01653684,0.03021506,-0.01395424,-0.05195507,0.01916058,-0.01792263,0.0120733,-0.01256009,-0.00732445,0.04870894,0.04377298,0.07394052,0.02598676,-0.01993828,-0.03487546,-0.03824709,-0.0211823,-0.00413404,-0.03581363,0.01886351,0.04500761,0.01469448,0.00340625,0.05520101,0.04286816,0.05525231,0.02845737,0.04905097,0.03090169,-0.21182406,0.0593637,0.03508327,-0.02676361,-0.02828859,-0.05937346,0.03552676,0.05223761,-0.03388654,0.01147955,-0.00156211,0.01667876,0.02965037,-0.02204622,0.03249082,-0.03424759,-0.02353665,-0.05763781,-0.0119707,0.08022989,0.00365466,0.00529047,-0.0161415,0.03460473,0.02103367,-0.05919293,-0.01461723,-0.01401597,0.02410013,-0.02270524,0.03978449,0.03822338,-0.00404281,0.02111453,-0.01500727,0.02839603,-0.05554428,0.08427109,-0.03467547,0.00012758,0.02515295,-0.02816305,0.03355619,-0.0352149,-0.00219918,-0.04599673,-0.01734519,-0.00054468,-0.06743344,0.00661457,0