ks: The Hidden Existential Risk of AI","target":"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00146-025-02397-5","line":267},{"title":"Algorithm Aversion","target":"https://thedecisionlab.com/reference-guide/psychology/algorithm-aversion","line":269},{"title":"AI Boss Effect Report","target":"https://www.resume-now.com/job-resources/careers/ai-boss-effect-report","line":271},{"title":"How People Use & Trust ChatGPT in 2025","target":"https://expresslegalfunding.com/chatgpt-study/","line":273},{"title":"A quarter of Gen Zers have followed ChatGPT's career advice","target":"https://fortune.com/2025/08/19/quarter-of-gen-z-have-followed-ai-chatgpt-career-advice-and-few-have-regrets/","line":275},{"title":"AI and the future of human decision-making","target":"https://www.deloitte.com/us/en/insights/topics/talent/human-capital-trends/2026/decision-making-with-ai.html","line":277}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
